hadiths[93]{hadithnumber,text}:
1951,"Naafe ne Hazrat Abdullah (bin umr (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : jab tum mein se koi shakhs Jumey ke liye aaney ka irada karey to wo ghusl kare."
1952,"Leis ne ibne-Shahab se, unhon-ne Abdullah bin-Abdullah-bin Umer se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne member par khadey huey farmaya : tum mein se jo Jumey ke liye aaey ghusl kare."
1953,"ibne-Juraij ne kaha : ibne-Shahab ne Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ke donon beton Salim aur Abdullah se khabar di, unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se us (pichhli hadis) ke maaninde-riwaayat ki."
1954,"Yunus ne ibne-Shahab se, unhon-ne Salim bin-Abdullah se aur unhon-ne apne walid se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna. padhi. ( aagey ( usi (pichhli hadis) ki tarah hai."
1955,"Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Hazrat umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) Jumey ke din logon ko khitab farma rahe they (ke isi beech mein) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sahaba (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen) mein se aik shakhs dakhil hua, Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein awaz di : ( aaney ki) ye kon si ghadi hai? unhon-ne kaha : main aaj masroof ho gaya, ghar lauttey hi maine azan suni aur sirf wuzu kya (aur hazir ho gaya hon (Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : aur wo bhi) sirf ( wuzu ? halanke aapko malum hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ghusl karne ka hukm detey they."
1956,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : (eik baar (Hazrat umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) Jumey ke din logon ko khutba irshad farma rahe they ke usi doran mein Hazrat Usman-bin-Affan (Raziallahu anhu) masjid mein dakhil huey. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne un par aetraz kya aur kaha : logon ko kya hua ke azan ke baad der lagaatey hain? Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : aey ameerul-momeneen ! maine azan sunney par us se zyada kuchh nahi kya ke wuzu kya hai aur hazir ho gaya hun, is par umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha aur wo bhi) sirf ( wuzu ? kya tum logon ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey nahi suna : jab tum mein se koi Jumey ke liye aaey to wo ghusl karey?"
1957,Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Jumey ke din har baligh shakhs par ghusl karna wajib hai.
1958,"Urwa-bin-Zubair ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Jumey ke liye log apne gharon se aur awali se baari-baari aatey they wo ooni abaaein pahney hotey they aur (rastey mein) un par gardo-ghubar bhi padta tha jiski wjah se unse bu phootti thi unmein se aik insan Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur us waqt Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mere yahan tashrif farma they, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : kya hi achchha ho ke tum log us din ke liye saaf suthrey ho jaya karo."
1959,"Umra ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : log kaam-kaaj waley they unke naukar-chaakar na hotey they wo aisey they ke unse bu aati thi to unse kaha gaya : kya hi achchha ho ke tum Jumey ke din naha liya karo."
1960,"Saeed bin abi Bilal aur Bukair-bin-Ashajj ne Abu-Bakar bin Munkadir se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Amr bin Sulaim se unhon-ne Abdur-Rehman bin abi Saeed Khudri se aur unhon-ne apne walid (Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Jumey ke din ghusl karna har baligh shakhs par wajib hai aur miswak karna bhi aur (har shakhs) apni istitaat ke mutabiq khushbu istemal kare. albatta Bukair ne (sanad mein) Abdur-Rehman ka zikr nahi kya aur khushbu ke barey mein kaha : chahey wo aurat ki khushbu kyon na ho."
1961,Rooh bin Ubada aur Abdur-Razzaq ne ibne-Juraij se hadis bayan ki unhon-ne kaha mujhey Ibrahim bin Maisra ne Taaus se khabar di aur unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne Jumey ke din ghusl karne ke barey mein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka farman bayan kya. Taaus ne kaha : maine Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha : agar iske ghar walon ke paas maujood ho to wo khushbu ya tel bhi istemal kar sakta hai? unhon-ne ( jawab mein) kaha : main ye baat nahi janta.
1962,Muhammad-bin-Bakr aur Suhak bin Mukhlid donon ne ibne-Juraij se isi sanad ke sath (pichhli) hadis bayan ki.
1963,Taaus ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki aap ne farmaya : har musalman par Allah Taala ka haq hai ke wo har saat (7) dinon main (kam se kam ( aik baar nahaaey apna sar aur apna jism dhoey.
1964,Abu-Saleh Samaan ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jisne Jumey ke din ghusle-janabat ( jaisa ghusl ( kya phir (masjid ( chala gaya to usne mano aik oont qurbaan kya aur jo dusri ghadi mein gaya to mano us ne gaaey qurbaan ki aur jo teesri ghadi mein gaya bhale hi ya us ne seengon wala aik mendha qurbaan kya aur jo chothi ghadi mein gaya us ne bhale hi ya aik murgh Allah ke taqreeb ke liye pesh kya aur jo paanchwein ghadi mein gaya us ne bhale hi ya aik andaa taqreeb ke liye pesh kya iske baad jab imam aa jata hai to Farishtey zikr ( ibadat aur umur (baton) khair ki yad dahaani) suntey hain.
1965,"Qutaiba-bin-Saeed aur Muhammad-bin Rumeh bin muhajir ne hadis bayan ki, ibne- Rumeh ne kaha : hamein Leis ne Aqeel-bin-Khalid se khabar di unhon-ne ibne-Shahab se riwayat ki unhon-ne kaha mujhey Saeed-bin-Musaiyab ne khabar di ke Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein bataya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Jumey ke din jab imam khutba de raha ho (is waqt) agar tum ne apne sathi se kaha : khamosh raho to tum ne fuzool goi ki."
1966,Abdul-Malik bin Shuaib bin Leis ne kaha : mujh se mere walid Shuaib ne mere dada Leis se hadis bayan ki unhon-ne kaha : mujh se Aqeel-bin-Khalid ne ibne-Shahab se unhon-ne Umar-bin Abdul-Azeez se unhon-ne Abdullah-bin Ibrahim bin qaariz se riwayat ki neez unhon ( ibne-Shahab Zohri ( ne ibne-Musaiyab se bhi riwayat ki un donon ( Umar-bin Abdul-Azeez aur Saeed-bin-Musaiyab ( ne un ( ibne-Shahab se hadis bayan ki ke Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko farmatey suna. padhi. ( aagey isi sanad hadis) ki tarah hai.
1967,ibne-Juraij ne kaha : ibne-Shahab ne mujhey us hadis ki donon sanadon ke sath us hadis mein usi ki tarah khabar di albatta ibne-Juraij ne ( Abdullah-bin Ibrahim bin qaariz ke bajaey) Ibrahim bin-Abdullah-bin qaariz kaha hai. (Imam Muslim ne naam ki durusti ke liye ye sanad bayan ki)
1968,abu Zinad ne Aaraj se unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Jumey ke din jab imam khutba de raha ho (is waqt) agar tum ne apne sathi se kaha : khamosh raho to tum ne ( khud ( shor machaya. abu Zinad ne kaha : ye ( فقد لغيت) Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) (ke qabeeley ( ki lughat hai jabke ( aam murawwij lughat ( (  فقد لغوت ) hai.
1969,Yahya-bin-Yahya aur Qutaiba-bin-Saeed ne Malik-bin-Anas se unhon-ne abu Zinad se unhon-ne Aaraj se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Jumey ka zikr kartey huey farmaya : usmein aik ghadi hai us ( ghadi ( ki muwafiqat kartey huey koi musalman banda Namaz padhtey huey Allah Taala se jo kuchh bhi mangta hai Allah Taala usey ata kar deta hai. Quteba ne apni riwayat mein izafa kya : Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne hath se ishara farma kar us ghadi ke qaleel honey ko waazeh kya.
1970,Ayub ne Muhammad se unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki unhon-ne kaha : abul-Qaasim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : beshak Jumey ke din mein aik ghadi hai koi musalman bhi khada Namaz padhtey huey uski muwafiqat kar leta (usey pa leta) hai (aur) Allah Taala se kisi khair ka sawal karta hai to Allah Taala usey wahi ( khair ( ata kar deta hai. aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hath se iske qaleel aur kam honey ko bayan kya.
1971,"Ibne-Aun ne Muhammad se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki unhon-ne kaha abul-Qaasim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, padhi. ( aagey ( usi (pichhli hadis) ki tarah hai."
1972,"Salma bin Alqama ne Muhammad se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki unhon-ne kaha : abul-Qaasim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, padhi. ( aagey ( usi (pichhli hadis) ki tarah hai"
1973,Muhammad-bin-Ziyad ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki. aap ne farmaya Jumey ke din mein aik ghadi aisi hai ke koi musalman Allah Taala se kisi khair ka sawal kartey huey uski muwafiqat nahi karta magar Allah Taala usey wahi khair ata kar deta hai farmaya ye aik chhoti si ghadi hai.
1974,"Hammam-bin-Munabba ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki lekin unhon-ne 'wo aik chhoti si ghadi hai' nahi kaha,"
1975,abu-Burda bin abi Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai kaha : mujh se Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : kya tum ne apne walid ko Jumey ki ghadi ke barey mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se hadis bayan kartey huey suna hai? kaha : maine kaha : ji haan maine unhein ye kehtey suna hai ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna aap farma rahe they : ye imam ke baithney se lekar Namaz mukammal honey tak hai.
1976,ibne-Shahab ne kaha : mujhey Abdur-Rehman Aaraj ne khabar di unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ko kehtey suna ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : behtreen din jis par suraj tuloo hota hai Jumey ka din hai isi din Adam (Alaihissalam) paida kiye gaey aur isi din jannat mein dakhil kiye gaey aur isi din us se nikaley gaey.
1977,abu Zinad ne Aaraj se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : behtreen din jis mein suraj nikalta hai Jumey ka hai isi din Adam (Alaihissalam) ko paida kya gaya tha aur isi din unhein jannat mein dakhil kya gaya aur usi mein unhein us se nikala gaya (zamin ki khilafat saunpi gai) aur qiyamat bhi Jumey ke din hi barpaa hogi. ( Saleh mominon ke liye ye bada inaam hasil karne ka din hoga.)
1978,Amr Naqid ne kaha : hamein Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne abu Zinad se hadis sunai unhon-ne Aaraj se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ham sabse aakhiri hain aur qiyamat ke din sabse pahley hongey ye iske bawajud hai ke har ummat ko kitab ham se pahley di gaee aur hamein ( hamari kitab ( unke baad di gaee phir ye din jisey Allah Taala ne hamarey liye likh diya tha Allah Taala ne uske liye hamari rahnumai farmai log us mamley mein hamarey baad hain yahood kal (Jumey se aglaa din yani hafta manaaeingey) aur nasara parson (haftey se aglaa din itwaar ka manaaeingey.)
1979,ibne-abi-Umar ne kaha : hamein Sufiyan ne abu Zinad se hadis sunai unhon-ne Aaraj se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki neez ( Sufiyan ne Abdullah (bin Taaus se unhon-ne apne walid ( Taaus bin kaisaan ( se unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ham sab ke baad aaney waley hain aur qiyamat ke din ham sabse pahley hongey. padhi. usi ( uper zikr ki gaee hadis) ki tarah hai.
1980,Abu-Saleh ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ham aakhiri hain ( phir bhi) qiyamat ke din pahley hongey aur ham hi pahley jannat mein dakhil hongey albatta unhein (unki ( kitab ham sabse pahley di gaee aur hamein (hamari kitab) unke baad di gaee unhon-ne (aapas mein) ikhtilaf kya aur Allah Taala ne hamari us haq ki taraf rahnumai farmai jis mein unhon-ne ikhtilaf kya tha ye ( Juma ( unka wahi din tha jiske barey mein unhon-ne ikhtilaf kya Allah Taala ne hamein uski taraf rahnumai kar di. padhi. rawi ne kaha : Jumey ka din murad hai. aaj ka din hamara hai aur kal ka din yahudiyon ka hai us se agla din esaiyon kaa.
1981,Wahab-bin-Munabba ke bhai Hammam-bin-Munabba ne kaha : ye hadis hai jo Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne hamein Muhammad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bayan ki unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ham aakhiri hain ( magar ( qiyamat ke din sabqat ley janey waley hongey iske bawajud ke un logon ko ham se pahley kitab di gaee aur hamein unke baad di gaee aur ye ( Juma ( unka wahi din hai jawan par farz kya gaya tha aur wo iske barey mein ikhtilaf mein pad gaey phir Allah Taala ne iske barey mein hamari rehnumai farmai isliye wo log us ( ibadat ke din ke) mamley mein ham se peechhey hain yahood ( apna din) kal manaaein gey aur Esai parson .
1982,"abu-Kuraib aur Wasil bin Abdul-Aala ne kaha : ham se ibne-Fuzail ne abu-Malik Ashjai (Sad-bin-Tariq) se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne abu-Hazim se aur unhon-ne Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, neez unhon (abu-Malik) ne Rabai-bin-Hirash se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, un donon (sahaabiyon) ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jo log ham se pahley they Allah Taala ne unhein Juma ki raah se hata diya, isliye yahood ke liye haftey ka din ho gaya aur nasara ke liye itwaar ka din. phir Allah Taala hamein (is duniya mein laya (aur Jumey ke din ki taraf hamari rehnumai farma di. us ne Juma phir hafta phir itwaar rakha (jis tarah wo ibadat ke dinon mein ham se peechhey hain) isi tarah qiyamat ke din bhi ham se peechhey hongey. ahle-duniya mein se ham sab ke baad hain aur qiyamat ke din sabse pahley hongey. jinka faisla ( baqi ( makhlooqat se pahley kar diya jaeyga Wasil ki riwayat main ( المقضي لهم ( ki jagah ( ) المقضي بينهم ( ) jinke darmyan faisla ( hai."
1983,"ibne-abi-Zayda ne ( abu-Malik ( Sad-bin-Tariq se khabar di, unhon-ne kaha : Rabai-bin-Hirash ne mujhey Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : hamari rehnumai Jumey ki taraf ki gaee aur jo log ham se pahley they unko Allah Taala ne us se dusri raah par laga diya. aagey ibne-Fuzail ke ham mana hadis bayan ki."
1984,"abu-Adbullah Agharr ne khabar di ke unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo keh rahe they : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya jab Jumey ka din hota hai to masjid ke darwazon mein se har darwazey par Farishtey hotey hain jo ( aaney walon ki tarteeb ke mutabiq (pahley phir pahley ka naam likhtey hain, aur jab imam ( member par) baith jata hai to wo (naamon waale) saheefey lapet detey hain aur aakar zikr ( khutba ( suntey hain. aur garmi mein (pahley ( aaney waley ki misal us insan jaisi hai jo oont qurbaan karta hai phir (jo aaya ( maano wo gaaey qurbaan kar deta hai. phir (jo aaya ( maano wo mendha qurbaan kar deta hai, phir (jo aaya ( maano wo taqreeb ke liye murghi pesh karta hai phir (jo aaya ( maano wo taqreeb ke liye andaa pesh karta hai."
1985,Saeed (bin Musaiyab ( ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se isi (pichhli hadis) ki tarah riwayat ki.
1986,"Suhel ke walid Abu-Saleh Samaan ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : masjid ke darwazon mein se har aik darwazey par aik farishta hota hai jo pahley phir pahley aaney waley ka naam likhta hai. aap ne oont ki qurbani ki misal di, phir batadreej kam kartey gaey yahan tak ke) aakhir mein) andey jaisey chhotey ( sadqey ( ki misal di. phir jab imam member par baith jata hai to ( indraaj ke) saheefey lapet diye jatey hain aur) Farishtey ( zikr w nasihat ( sunney (ke liye hazir ho jatey hain."
1987,"Suhel ne apne walid ( Abu-Saleh ( se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke aap ne farmaya : jisne ghusl kya, phir Jumey ke liye hazir hua, phir iske muqaddar mein jitni ( nafl ( Namaz thi padhi, phir khamoshi se ( khutba ( sunta raha yahan tak ke khateeb apne khutbey se farigh ho gaya, phir iske sath Namaz padhi, iske us Jumey se lekar aik aur) pichhley ya agley ( Jumey tak ke gunah bakhsh diye jatey hain aur mazeed teen dinon ke bhi."
1988,"Aamash ne Abu-Saleh se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jis shakhs ne wuzu kya aur achchi tarah wuzu kya, phir Jumey ke liye aaya, ghaur ke sath khamoshi se khutba suna, iske Jumey se lekar Jumey tak gunah maaf kar diye jatey hain. aur teen din zayed ke bhi. aur jo ( bila wajah ( kankariyon ko hath lagata raha (unse khelta raha), us ne bekar aur Fuzool kaam kya."
1989,"Hasan-bin- Ayash ne Jafar bin-Muhammad se, unhon-ne apne walid ( Muhammad ( se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Namaz padhtey they, phir wapas aatey , phir apne pani laney waley oonton ko aaraam ka waqt detey, Hasan ne kaha : maine Jafar se kaha : ye (namaz ( kis waqt hoti? unhon-ne kaha : suraj ke dhalney ke waqt."
1990,"Qasim bin Zakariya ne kaha : hamein Khalid-bin Mukhlid ne hadis bayan ki, neez Abdullah-bin Abdur-Rehman darmi ne kaha : hamein Yahya bin Hassan ne hadis bayan ki, un donon ( Khalid aur Yahya ( ne kaha : hamein Sulaiman-bin Bilal ne Jafar se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne apne walid ( Muhammad ( se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kis waqt Juma padhtey they? unhon-ne kaha : aap Juma padhatey , phir ham oonton ke paas jatey, phir unhein aaraam ka waqt detey. Abdullah ne apni riwayat mein ye izafa kya : jis waqt suraj dhal jata. ( jimaal ( se murad ( ) nawaazeh ( , yani pani laney waley oont hain."
1991,"Abdullaah-bin-Muslima bin Qanab, Yahya-bin-Yahya aur Ali-bin hijr mein se Yahya ne kaha : hamein khabar di aur doosrey donon ne kaha : ham se hadis bayan ki Abdul-Azeez bin abi Hazim ne apne walid abu-Hazim se, unhon-ne Hazrat Suhel (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : ham Juma ke baad hi qailula kartey aur khana khaatey they. ( Ali ( ibne- hijr ne izafa kya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ahade-mubarak mein."
1992,"Wakee ne Yala-bin-Haaris Maharibi se riwayat ki, unhon-ne Ayas bin Salma-bin-Akwa se aur unhon-ne apne walid (Hazrat Salma-bin-Akwa (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : jab suraj dhalta ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Juma padhtey , phir ham saaya talash kartey huey laut'tey."
1993,Hisham bin Abdul-Malik ne Yala bin-Haaris se baqi bachi isi sanad ke sath riwayat ki ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Juma padhtey phir laut'tey to hamein diwaron ka itna bhi saaya na milta ke ham (suraj se) uski ot ley sakein .
1994,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Jumey ke din khadey ho kar khutba irshad farmatey, phir ( thodi der ( baith jatey, phir khadey ho jatey. kaha : jis tarah aajkal ( khutba dene waale) kartey hain."
1995,"abu-Ahwas ne Samak se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir bin samra (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke 2 khutbey hotey they jinke darmyan aap baithtey they. aap Quran padhtey aur logon ko nasihat aur tazkeer farmatey."
1996,"abu khaisma ne Samak se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Hazrat Jaabir bin samra (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujhey khabar di ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khadey ho kar khutba detey they, phir baith jatey, phir khadey hotey aur khadey ho kar khutba detey, isliye jisne tumhen ye bataya ke aap baith kar khutba detey they, us ne jhoot bola. Allah ki qasam! maine aap ke sath 2 hazaar se zayed namazein padhi hain. (jin mein bahut se Jumey bhi aaey aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne tamam khutbey khadey ho kar diye.)"
1997,"Jarir ne Husain-bin-Abdur-Rehman se riwayat ki, unhon-ne Saalim-bin-abi-Jaad se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Jumey ke din khadey ho kar khutba de rahe they ke Sham (Syria) se aik tijarati qaafila aa gaya, logon ne iska rukh kar liya yahan tak ke peechhey baara aadmiyon ke siwa koi na bacha to ye aayat nazil ki gaee jo sura Juma mein hai : aur jab wo tijarat ya koi mashghala dekhtey hain to uski taraf toot padtey hain aur aapko khada chhod jatey hain."
1998,"Abdullah-bin-Idris ne Husain se isi sanad ke sath riwayat ki, kaha : (jab tijarati qaafila aaya to ( Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khutba de rahe they. ye nahi kaha : khadey huey."
1999,"Khalid Tahan ne Husain se riwayat ki, unhon-ne Salim aur abu Sufiyan se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : ham Jumey ke din Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath they ke aik chhota sa bazar ( saman bechney walon ka qaafila ( aa gaya to log uski taraf nikal gaey aur) sirf ( baara aadmiyon ke siwa koi na bacha , main bhi unmein tha, kaha : is par Allah Taala ne ye aayat utari : aur jab wo tijarat ya koi mashghala dekhtey hain to uski taraf toot padtey hain aur aapko khada chhod detey hain aayat ke aakhir tak."
2000,"Hushaim ne kaha : hamein Husain ne abu Sufiyan aur Saalim-bin abi Jaad se khabar di, unhon-ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne bayan kya, aik baar jab Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Jumey ke din khadey huey ( khutba de rahe ( they ke aik tijarati qaafila Madina aa gaya, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sathi uski taraf lapak padey yahan tak ke aap ke sath baara aadmiyon ke siwa koi na bacha . unmein Abu-Bakar aur umr (Raziallahu anhu) bhi maujood they. kaha : to (us par) ye aayat utri : aur jab wo tijarat ya koi mashghala dekhtey hain to uski taraf toot padtey hain."
2001,"Hazrat Kab-bin-Ujra (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke wo masjid mein aaey, dekha ke (umwi waali) Abdur-Rehman bin Umme-Hakam baith kar khutba de raha hai, unhon-ne farmaya : is khabees ko dekho , baith kar khutba de raha hai, jabke Allah Taala ka farman hai : aur jab wo tijarat ya koi mashghala dekhtey hain to idhar toot padtey hain aur aapko khada chhod jatey hain."
2002,Hakam bin Mina ne hadis bayan ki kaha : Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar aur Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein hadis bayan ki ke unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna aap apne member ki lakdiyon par) khadey huey) farma rahe they logon ke giroh har sura Juma chhod deney se baaz aa jayen ya Allah Taala unke dilon par mohar laga dega phir wo ghaafilon mein se ho jaengey.
2003,abwaa hosh ne Samak bin Harab se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir bin Samra (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki unhon-ne kaha : main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Namaz padhta tha aap ki Namaz (tawaalat mein) mutwassit (darmiyani) hoti thi aur aap ka khutba bhi mutwassit hota tha.
2004,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba aur ibne-Numair ne kaha : hamein Muhammad-bin-Bishr ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Zakariya ne hadis bayan ki kaha : mujh se Samak-bin-Harab ne Hazrat Jaabir bin Samra (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : main namazein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath padhta tha to aap ki Namaz darmiyani hoti thi aur aap ka khutba bhi darmiyana hota tha abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba ki riwayat main ( Zakariya ne kaha : mujhey Samak-bin-Harab ne hadis bayan ki ke bajaey) ( Zakariya ( ne mujhey Samak se riwayat ki ke alfaz hain."
2005,"Abdul Wahab bin abdul Majeed ( Saqafi ( ne Jafar ( sadiq ( bin-Muhammad ( Baaqar ( se riwayat ki unhon-ne apne walid se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab khutba detey to aap ki aankhen surkh ho jatin, awaz buland ho jati aur jalal ki kaifiyat tari ho jati thi yahan tak ke aisa lagta jaisey aap kisi lashkar se dara rahe hain farma rahe hain ke wo ( lashakr) subah ya Sham ( tak) tumhen aa lega aur farmatey, main aur qiyamat is tarah bhejey gaey hain aur aap apni shahadat ki ungli aur darmyani ungli ko mila kar dikhatey aur farmatey. (Hamdo-Salat (Durud) (ke baad bila shubah behtreen hadis ( kalam ( Allah ki kitab hai aur zindagi ka behtreen tariqa Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka tariqa zindagi hai aur) Deen mein) bad tareen kaam wo hain jo khud nikaley gaey hon aur har nayaa nikala hua kaam gumrahi hai phir farmatey : main har momin ke sath khud uski nisbat zyada mohabbat aur shafqat rakhney wala hun. jo koi ( momin apne baad) maal chhod gaya to wo uske ahal w ayaal ( waarison (ka hai aur jo momin qarz ya be sahara ahal w ayaal chhod gaya to (us qarz ko) meri taraf lotaya jaey (aur uske kunbey ki parwarish ( mere zimmey hai."
2006,Sulaiman-bin-Bilal ne kaha : mujh se Jafar-bin-Muhammad ne apne walid se riwayat ki unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se suna wo kehtey they Jumey ke din Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka khutba is tarah hota tha ke aap Allah Taala ki hamd w sana bayan kartey phir iske baad aap (apni baat ( irshad farmatey aur aap ki awaz bahut buland hoti . phir us (pichhli hadis) ki tarah hadis bayan ki.
2007,Sufiyan ne Jafar se unhon-ne apne walid ( Muhammad Baaqar ( se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) logon ko (is tarah) khutba detey pahley Allah ki shaan ke mutabiq uski hamd w sana bayan kartey phir farmatey. jisey Allah seedhi raah par chalaey usey koi gumrah nahi kar sakta aur jisey wo seedhi raah se hata de usey koi hidayat nahi de sakta aur behtreen baat ( hadis) Allah ki kitab hai. padhi. aagey ( Abdul Wahab bin abdul Majeed) Saqafi ki hadis ( 2005 ( ki tarah hai.
2008,"Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke zamad Makka aaya, wo ( qabila ( Azd shanu se tha aur aaseb ka dam kya karta tha ( jisey log reeh kehtey they, yani aisi hawa jo nazar nahi aati , asar karti hai) us ne Makka ke be-waqufon ko ye kehtey suna ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko junoon ho gaya hai (nauzu-billah) usne kaha : agar main us aadmi ko dekh loon to shayad Allah Taala usey mere hathon shifa bakhsh de. kaha : wo aap se mila aur kehney laga : aey Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! main is nazar na aaney wali bimari ( reeh ( ko zaayel karne ke liye dam karta hun aur Allah Taala jisey chahta hai mere hathon shifa bakhshta hai to aap kya chahtey hain (ke mein dam karun?) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ( jawab mein) kaha : (ان الحمد لله نحمده ونستعينه من يهده الله فلا مضل له ومن يضلل فلا هادي له واشهد ان لا اله الا الله وحده لا شريك له وان محمدا عبده ورسوله اما بعد ) yaqinan tamam hamd Allah ke liye hai, ham usi ki hamd kartey hain aur usi se madad maangtey hain, jis ko Allah seedhi raah par chalaaey, usey koi gumrah nahi kar sakta aur jisey wo gumrah chhod de, usey koi raahe-raast par nahi la sakta aur main gawahi deta hun ke Allah ke siwa koi sachcha maabood nahi, wahi akela ( maabood ( hai, iska koi Sharik nahi aur bila shubah Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) uska banda aur uska rasool hai, iske baad ! kaha : wo bol utha : apne ye kalimaat mujhey dobara sunaein . Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne teen martaba ye kalimaat uske samney dohraaey. is par usne kaha : maine kaahinon, jadugaron aur shaairon (sab (ke qaul suney hain, maine aap ke un kalimaat jaisa koi kalima (kabhi) nahi suna, ye to bahar ( balaaghat ( ki teh tak pahunch gaey hain aur kehney laga : hath badhaaiye ! main aap ke sath Islam par bait karta hun. kaha : to usne aap ki bait kar li. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aur teri ( taraf se teri ( qaum (ke Islam ( par bhi (teri bait leta hun ( usne kaha : apni qaum (ke Islam ( par bhi) bait karta hun) iske baad aap ne aik sariya ( chhota lashakr) bheja , wo unki qaum ke paas se guzrey to ameer lashkar ne lashkar se puchha : kya tum ne un logon se koi cheez li hai? to logon mein se aik shakhs ne kaha : maine unse aik lota liya hai usne kaha : usey wapas kar do kyonke ye (koi aur nahi balke) zamaad (Raziallahu anhu) ki qaum hai."
2009,"abu-Waail ne kaha : hamarey samney Hazrat Ammar (Raziallahu anhu) ne khutba diya. intihai mukhtasar aur intihai baleegh ( baat ki) jab wo member se utrey to ham ne kaha : abu-Yaqzaan ! aap ne intihai asardar aur intihai mukhtasar khutba diya hai, kash! ! aap saans kuchh lambi kar letey ( zyada der baat kar letey ( unhon-ne farmaya : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey huey suna hai : insan ki Namaz ka lamba hona aur us ke khutbey ka chhota hona uski samajhdari ki alamat hai, isliye Namaz lambi karo aur khutba chhota do, aur is mein koi shuba nahi ke koi bayan jaadoo (ki tarah) hota hai."
2010,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba aur Muhammad-bin-Abdullah bin Numer ne kaha : hamein Wakee ne Sufiyan se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Abdul-Azeez bin Raafe se, unhon-ne Tameem bin tarfa se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Adi-bin Hatim (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke aik shakhs ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney khutba diya aur (is mein) kaha : jo Allah aur uske rasool ki itaat karta hai us ne rushd w hidayat pa li aur jo in donon ki nafarmani karta hai wo bhatak gaya. is par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : to bura khateeb hai, ( fiqrey ke pahley hissey ki tarah) yun kaho , jisne Allah ki aur uske rasool ki nafarmani ki (wo gumrah hua. ( ibne-Numair ki riwayat main ( ghawi) hai."
2011,"Safwan ke walid Hazrat Yala bin Umayya (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, aap member par padh rahe they : ( وَنَادَوْا يَا مَالِكُ (aur wo pukaarengey : aey Malik! ( الزخرف 77 : 43 ("
2012,"Sulaiman-bin Bilal ne Yahya-bin-Saeed se riwayat ki, unhon-ne Umra binte-Abdur-Rehman (bin Sad bin Zarara ansariya ( se, unhon-ne ( maa ki taraf se) apni behan se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine sura (ق padhi. وَالْقُرْ‌آنِ الْمَجِيدِ) Jumey ke din Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki zaban Mubarak se sun kar yad ki. aap usey har Jumey member par padh kar sunaya (aur samjhaya) kartey they."
2013,"Yahya bin Ayub ne Yahya-bin-Saeed se, unhon-ne Umra se aur unhon-ne apni behan se jo umr mein unse badi thin, riwayat ki. Sulaiman-bin Bilal ki hadis ki tarah ."
2014,"Abdullah-bin Muhammad-bin Maan (معن) ne Harisa bin Nauman ki beti ( Umme- Hisham ( se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine sura Qaaf (kisi aur se nahi seedhey-seedhey) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki zaban se sun kar yad ki, aap har Jumey mein usey padh kar Khattab farmatey they. unhon-ne kaha : hamara aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka tandoor aik hi tha."
2015,"Yahya bin-Abdullah-bin Abdur-Rehman bin Sad bin Zarara ne Umme- Hisham binte- Harisa bin Nauman (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : hamara aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka tandoor 2 ya aik saal se kuchh zyada arsa aik hi raha aur maine sura Qaf ( kisi aur se nahi balke) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki zaban se sun kar yad ki, aap har Jumey ke din jab logon ko khutba detey to usey member par padhtey they."
2016,"Abdullah-bin-Idris ne Husain se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Umara bin Rubiya ( Saqafi ( (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : unhon-ne Bishr bin Marwan (bin-Hakam, aamile-Madina) ko member par) taqreer ke doran ( donon hath buland kartey dekha to kaha : Allah Taala un donon hathon ko bigaadey , maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha ke aap apne hath se isse zyada ishara nahi kartey they aur apni angusht shahadat se ishara kya."
2017,"abu-Awana ne Husain-bin-Abdur-Rehman se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Jumey ke din Bishr bin Marwan ko donon hath uthatey huey dekha to is par Umara bin Rubiya (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha, iske baad us (uper zikr ki gaee riwayat) ke ham mana riwayat bayan ki."
2018,"Hammad-bin-Zaid ne Amr-bin-Dinar se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : usi beech mein jab Jumey ke din Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khutba de rahe they aik aadmi (masjid mein) aaya to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us se puchha : aey falan ( naam liya ( ! kya tu ney Namaz padh li hai? usne kaha : nahi. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : utho aur Namaz padho ."
2019,"Ayub ne Amr (bin Dinar) se, unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se Hammad ki tarah riwayat ki, aur unhon ( Ayub ( ne bhi usmein 2 rakaat ka zikr nahi kya ( albatta agli riwayat mein Sufiyan ne kya hai.)"
2020,"Qutaiba-bin-Saeed aur Ishaq-bin-Ibrahim mein se Quteba ne kaha : hamein hadis sunai aur Ishaq ne kaha : hamein khabar di Sufiyan ne Amr se, unhon-ne Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo keh rahe they : aik aadmi masjid mein dakhil hua jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Jumey ke din khutba de rahe they. to aap ne puchha : kya tum ne Namaz padh li ? usne kaha : nahi. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : utho aur 2 rakatein padh lo. Quteba ki hadis main (فصل ركعتين) ke bajaey) (صل ركعتين) ( 2 rakatein padho ( hai."
2021,"ibne-Juraij ne kaha : hamein Amr-bin-Dinar ne khabar di ke unhon-ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo keh rahe they : aik aadmi aaya jabke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) member par they, Jumey ke din khutba irshad farma rahe they, to aap ne us se puchha : kya tum ne 2 rakatein padh li hain? usne kaha : nahi. aap ne farmaya : padh lo."
2022,"Shoba ne Amr (bin Dinar ( se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se suna ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khutbey mein farmaya : jab tum mein se koi shakhs Jumey ke din aaey jabke imam ( ghar se) nikal ( kar) aa chuka hai to wo 2 rakaat padh ley."
2023,"abu-Zubair ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Sulaik ghatfaani (Raziallahu anhu) Jumey ke din aaey jabke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) member par baithey huey they, to Sulaik Namaz padhney se pahley hi baith gaey. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse kaha : kya tum ne 2 rakatein padh li hain? unhon-ne kaha : nahi. aap ne farmaya : utho aur 2 rakatein padho ."
2024,"abu Sufiyan ( Talha-bin-Naafe waastii ( ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Sulaik ghatfaani (Raziallahu anhu) Jumey ke din (us waqt) aaey jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khutba de rahe they, to wo baith gaey. aap ne unse kaha : aey Sulaik !  uth kar do rakatein padho aur unmein ikhtisar barto . iske baad Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ! jab tum mein se koi Jumey ke din aaey jabke imam khutba de raha ho to wo do rakatein padhey aur unmein ikhtisar kare."
2025,"Hazrat abu-rifa'a ( Tameem-bin-Usaid Adwi (Raziallahu anhu)) ne kaha ke main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas (us waqt) pahuncha jabke aap khutba de rahe they, maine kaha : aey Allah ke rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ! aik pardesii aadmi hai apne Deen ke barey mein poochhney aaya hai. usey malum nahi ke uska diin kya hai? kaha : to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) meri taraf mutwajjeh huey aur apna khutba chhoda , yahan tak ke mere paas pahunch gaey. aik kursi laai gaee mere khayal mein iske paaey lohey ke they. kaha : to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) is par baith gaey aur Allah Taala ne jo kuchh aapko sikhaya tha usmein se mujhey sikhaney lagey phir apne khutbey ke liye badhey aur iska aakhiri hissey mukammal farmaya."
2026,"Sulaiman jo Hilal ( tamimi (ke betey hain, unhon-ne Jafar ( sadiq ( se, unhon-ne apne walid se aur unhon-ne abu-Raafe (Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke Maula ke betey Ubaidullah) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Marwan ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ko Madina mein apna jaa-nasheen muqarrar kya aur khud Makka chala gaya. Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne hamein Jumey ki Namaz padhai aur) pehli rakaat mein) sura Juma padhney ke baad dusri rakaat main ( إِذَا جَاءَكَ الْمُنَافِقُونَ ( padhi aur kaha : jab Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) Jumey ki Namaz se farigh huey to main unke paas ja pahuncha aur unse kaha : aap ne wo do soortein padhi hain jo Ali-ibne- taalib (Raziallahu anhu) Kufa mein padha kartey they. Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko Jumey ke din ye soortein padhtey huey suna hai."
2027,"Hatim-bin-Ismail aur Abdul-Azeez darawardi donon ne (apni-apni sanad ke saath) Jafar se riwayat ki, unhon-ne apne walid se aur unhon-ne Ubaidullah-bin-abi-Raafe se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Marwan ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ko qaaim maqam governer banaya. padhi. aagey usi ki tarah hai, siwaey iske ke Hatim ki riwayat (in alfaz ( mein hai : unhon-ne pehli rakaat mein sura Juma padhi aur dusri rakaat main sura munafiqin ( إِذَا جَاءَكَ الْمُنَافِقُونَ ( Abdul-Azeez ki riwayat Sulaiman-bin Bilal ki (pichhli ( riwayat ki tarah hai."
2028,"Jarir ne Ibrahim-bin-Muhammad-bin-muntashir se, unhon-ne apne walid se, unhon-ne Hazrat Noman-bin-Bashir ke aazad karda ghulam Habib-bin-Saalim se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Noman-bin-Bashir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) dono eidon aur Jumey main ''sura aala'' ( سَبِّحِ اسْمَ رَ‌بِّكَ الْأَعْلَى (aur ''sura ghashiyaa'' ( هَلْ أَتَاكَ حَدِيثُ الْغَاشِيَةِ ( padhtey . kaha : aur agar eid aur Juma aik hi din ikatthey ho jatey to aap yahi do soortein donon namazon mein padhtey they."
2029,abu-Awana ne Ibrahim-bin-Muhammad-bin muntashir se isi sanad ke sath (usi ki tarah ( riwayat ki.
2030,Ubaidullah-bin-Abdullah ne kaha : Suhak-bin-Qais ne Hazrat Noman-bin-Bashir (Raziallahu anhu) ko khat likh kar puchha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Jumey ke din sura Juma ke ilawa (aur ( kon si sura padhi ? unhon-ne jawab diya : Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ''sura ghashiyaa'' ( هَلْ أَتَاكَ حَدِيثُ الْغَاشِيَةِ ( padha kartey they.
2031,"Abda-bin-Sulaiman ne Sufiyan se riwayat ki, unhon-ne mukhawwal-bin-raashid se, unhon-ne Muslim-al-bateen se, unhon-ne Saeed-bin-Jubair se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Jumey ke din fajr ki Namaz main (الم padhi. تَنزِيلُ الْكِتَابِ) sura sajdaa aur sura dahar (هَلْ أَتَىٰ عَلَى الْإِنسَانِ حِينٌ مِّنَ الدَّهْرِ‌)  padhtey they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Jumey ki Namaz mein sura Juma aur sura munaafiqon padhtey they."
2032,Abdullah-bin-Numair aur Wakee donon ne Sufiyan se isi sanad ke sath usi (pichhli hadis) ki tarah riwayat ki.
2033,Shoba ne mukhawwal se isi sanad ke sath donon namazon ke barey mein usi (pichhli hadis) ki tarah riwayat ki jis tarah Sufiyan ne (apni riwayat mein) kaha.
2034,"Sufiyan ne Sad-bin-Ibrahim se, unhon-ne Abdur-Rehman Aaraj se, unhon-ne Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke aap Jumey ke din fajr ki Namaz main ( الم تَنزِيلُ الْكِتَابِ (aur ( هَلْ أَتَىٰ عَلَى الْإِنسَانِ ( padhtey they."
2035,"Ibrahim-bin-Sad ne apne walid ( Sad-bin-Ibrahim ( se, unhon-ne Abdur-Rehman Aaraj se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Jumey ke din subah ki Namaz ki pehli rakaat main ( الم تَنزِيلُ الْكِتَابِ (aur dusri rakaat main sura dahar ( هَلْ أَتَىٰ عَلَى الْإِنسَانِ حِينٌ مِّنَ الدَّهْرِ‌لَمْ يَكُن شَيْئًا مَّذْكُورً‌ا ( padhtey they."
2036,"Khalid-bin-Abdullaah ne Suhel se, unhon-ne apne walid ( Abu-Saleh ( se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab tum mein se koi Juma padh chukey to iske baad char rakatein padhey ."
2037,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba aur Amr-Naqid ne kaha : hamein Abdullah-bin-Idris ne Suhel se hadis sunai, unhon-ne apne walid se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab tum Jumey ke baad Namaz padho to char rakatein padho Amr ne apni riwayat mein izafa kya, ibne-Idrees ne kaha Suhel ne kaha : agar tumhen kisi cheez ki wjah se jaldi ho to do rakatein masjid mein padh lo aur do rakatein waapas ja kar (ghar mein) padh lo."
2038,"Jarir aur Sufiyan ne Suhel se, unhon-ne apne walid se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki. unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum mein se jo shakhs Jumey ke baad Namaz padhey to char rakatein padhey . Jarir ki hadis main ( منكم ( (tum mein se) ke alfaz nahi hain."
2039,Leis ne Naafe se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke jab wo Juma padh letey to wapas jatey aur apne ghar mein do rakatein padhtey . phir unhon ( ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu)) ne bataya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aisa hi kartey they.
2040,"Yahya-bin-Yahya ne kaha : maine Imam Malik par) hadis ki) qirat ki, unhon-ne Naafe se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki nafl Namaz ko bayan kya aur kaha ke aap Jumey ke baad koi ( nafl ( Namaz na padhtey yahan tak ke wapas tashrif ley jatey phir apne ghar mein do rakatein padhtey they. Yahya-bin-Yahya ne kaha : mera khayal hai ke maine (Imam Malik ke samney ( ) فيصلي ( padha tha ya yaqin hai (ke yahi padha tha)."
2041,Salim ne apne walid (Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat ki ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Jumey ke baad do rakatein padhtey they.
2042,"ghandar ne ibne-Juraij se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Umar-bin-ata-bin-abi khuwaar ne bataya ke Naafe-bin-Juber ne unhein namir ke bhaanjey Saaib ke paas bheja unse us cheez ke barey mein poochhney ke liye jo Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ne unki Namaz mein dekhi thi. Saaib ne kaha : haan , maine maqsoora (masjid ke hujrey ( mein unke sath Juma padha tha aur jab imam ne salam phera to main apni jagah par khada ho gaya aur Namaz padhi. jab Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) andar dakhil huey to mujhey bulwaya aur kaha : jo kaam tum ne kya hai aainda na karna. jab tum Juma padh lo to usey kisi dusri Namaz se na milaanaa yahan tak ke guftgu kar lo ya us jagah se nikal jao kyonke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein is baat ka hukm diya tha ke ham kisi Namaz ko dusri Namaz se na milaaein yahan tak ke ham guftgu kar lein ya (is jagah se) nikal jaaein."
2043,Hajjaj-bin-Muhammad ne kaha : ibne-Juraij ne kaha : mujhey Umar-bin-ata ne bataya ke Naafe-bin-Juber ne unhein namir ke bhaanjey saaib-bin-Yazeed ke paas bhejaa. padhi. aagey pichhli hadis ke ki manind (tarah) bayan kya. magar (is riwayat mein) ye hai ke Saaib ne kaha : jab unhon-ne salam phera to main apni jagah khada ho gaya. unhon-ne ( salam phera kaha (Imam ka zikr nahi kya.
